textBeforeTable: Track Listing Long before the horrible rash of fashion reality shows, Mr. Blackwell blazed the trail as a fasionista and celebrity critic back in the day. This album showcases smart smooth arrangements (check out "In Hollywood (Ballet)" along with Mr. Blackwell's vocal stylings.
